00:13:41,190 --> 00:13:43,550
I don't deserve to know?

288
00:13:43,710 --> 00:13:45,830
You don't like to be high-profile, right?

289
00:13:46,070 --> 00:13:47,470
Maybe he's afraid that you would be unhappy

290
00:13:47,470 --> 00:13:48,630
and force him to delete his post.

291
00:13:49,270 --> 00:13:51,190
It's just a post.

292
00:13:51,190 --> 00:13:52,750
Why would I be unhappy?

293
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:57,150
But he released a post and blocked his girlfriend.

294
00:13:57,150 --> 00:13:58,630
Everyone gets angry.

295
00:14:01,150 --> 00:14:04,030
It's too late to call him now.

296
00:14:04,070 --> 00:14:05,990
You major in journalism.

297
00:14:06,150 --> 00:14:08,070
Don't you know how fast the gossip travels?

298
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:09,310
Look.

299
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:13,630
Your relationship with Ling Chao is all over Moments.

300
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:15,310
Look, many people said

301
00:14:15,470 --> 00:14:16,910
you are going to live together.

302
00:14:17,670 --> 00:14:19,990
This one said you plan to get a marriage certificate.

303
00:14:20,070 --> 00:14:21,430
What marriage certificate?

304
00:14:21,430 --> 00:14:22,790
I'm not at the legal age for marriage.

305
00:14:22,790 --> 00:14:24,590
What are they thinking?

306
00:14:25,070 --> 00:14:27,390
No wonder Ling Chao is smart.

307
00:14:27,550 --> 00:14:29,510
He is using the public opinion to defeat Zhou Xingyu.

308
00:14:29,550 --> 00:14:30,590
If it's true,

309
00:14:30,750 --> 00:14:32,790
Zhou Xingyu will be the other man.

310
00:14:32,870 --> 00:14:36,150
You will be a bad girl and a traitor.

311
00:14:36,470 --> 00:14:38,590
What are you talking about?

312
00:14:39,670 --> 00:14:41,590
What time is it? Can't you see I'm sleeping?

313
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:42,950
Ling Chao.

314
00:14:43,470 --> 00:14:44,430
Wait and see.

315
00:15:01,750 --> 00:15:02,790
You still won't give up?

316
00:15:03,630 --> 00:15:05,430
What's the big deal about living together?

317
00:15:06,030 --> 00:15:07,390
As long as you are not married,

318
00:15:07,430 --> 00:15:08,630
I still have a chance.

319
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:14,670
I don't want your money.

320
00:15:15,870 --> 00:15:17,870
I bought this for Xiao Tu willingly.

321
00:15:19,070 --> 00:15:19,990
The delivery fee.

322
00:15:20,630 --> 00:15:21,430
Ling Chao.

323
00:15:21,590 --> 00:15:22,710
Why did you block me on your Moments?

324
00:15:22,710 --> 00:15:23,710
Explain it to me.

325
00:15:24,630 --> 00:15:25,470
Sister.

326
00:15:25,950 --> 00:15:27,470
You are having a fight with him?

327
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:28,670
Gosh.

328
00:15:28,950 --> 00:15:31,510
