334
00:15:45,550 --> 00:15:46,510
Are you okay?

335
00:15:46,590 --> 00:15:48,790
You really care about him more.

336
00:15:48,870 --> 00:15:50,510
I really envy you.

337
00:15:51,030 --> 00:15:52,390
You can attract her attention

338
00:15:52,390 --> 00:15:53,670
by making her angry.

339
00:15:54,430 --> 00:15:55,110
You are not like me.

340
00:15:55,110 --> 00:15:56,550
Whenever I see Xiao Tu,

341
00:15:56,830 --> 00:15:58,870
I will blush, and my heart will beat so fast. And I can't say a word.

342
00:15:59,750 --> 00:16:00,470
Sister.

343
00:16:01,550 --> 00:16:03,350
Am I useless?

344
00:16:03,670 --> 00:16:05,270
You said a lot.

345
00:16:05,830 --> 00:16:06,390
No.

346
00:16:07,390 --> 00:16:08,070
Baby.

347
00:16:08,470 --> 00:16:09,590
It's my fault.

348
00:16:09,750 --> 00:16:10,630
I'm not smooth-tongued.

349
00:16:10,990 --> 00:16:12,990
I can't say sweet words to make you happy.

350
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:14,870
Sister.

351
00:16:16,110 --> 00:16:17,830
Are you having hypoglycemia

352
00:16:17,830 --> 00:16:18,830
because you were angry and not in the mood to eat anything?

353
00:16:19,630 --> 00:16:21,230
It's my fault. I didn't take good care of you.

354
00:16:21,430 --> 00:16:23,230
This is the meal box I made for you.

355
00:16:23,590 --> 00:16:25,750
It might not be as good as what he bought for you.

356
00:16:25,990 --> 00:16:28,030
But if you are willing to taste it,

357
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:30,190
I'll be very happy.

358
00:16:32,230 --> 00:16:32,950
Baby.

359
00:16:34,070 --> 00:16:35,390
Did you not sleep well?

360
00:16:36,270 --> 00:16:37,990
I should have realized that you can't sleep well in the dorm.

361
00:16:38,270 --> 00:16:39,270
I should have...

362
00:16:40,630 --> 00:16:41,630
Shut up.

363
00:16:47,030 --> 00:16:47,790
Sister.

364
00:16:48,230 --> 00:16:49,470
Are you satisfied today?

365
00:16:49,990 --> 00:16:51,430
Why did you take me here today?

366
00:17:00,910 --> 00:17:01,990
It's so beautiful.

367
00:17:02,830 --> 00:17:04,390
QQ candies.

368
00:17:05,990 --> 00:17:07,390
Gosh, this sample room

369
00:17:07,390 --> 00:17:09,109
is exactly what I want.

370
00:17:10,710 --> 00:17:12,349
If you like it, buy it.

371
00:17:16,710 --> 00:17:19,310
I don't want this, this, and this.

372
00:17:19,349 --> 00:17:20,750
I'll buy the rest.

373
00:17:22,310 --> 00:17:23,510
Take these three.

374
00:17:23,950 --> 00:17:25,109
I already paid.

375
00:17:25,990 --> 00:17:28,510
A bossy president fell in love with me?

376
00:17:32,030 --> 00:17:32,950
My Lady.

377
00:17:33,150 --> 00:17:33,990
Are you satisfied?

378
00:17:37,070 --> 00:17:37,670
You...

379
00:17:38,110 --> 00:17:39,430
You really bought it?

380
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:42,870
Where did you get so much money?

381
00:17:43,870 --> 00:17:45,310
I made some money with Exclusive Fairy Tales.

382
00:17:45,670 --> 00:17:46,950
My parents gave me some.

383
00:17:48,390 --> 00:17:50,550
Why are you in such a hurry to buy a house?

384
00:17:53,230 --> 00:17:55,230
I'm going to Handuo as a trainee next semester.

385
00:17:56,110 --> 00:17:58,190
You want to work at Yunhai TV Station after graduation, right?

386
00:17:58,390 --> 00:17:59,870
It will be quite convenient for both of us if we live here.

387
00:18:01,550 --> 00:18:03,270
