389
00:18:06,870 --> 00:18:08,150
Because...

390
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:10,590
Because the things you chose

391
00:18:12,270 --> 00:18:13,950
are quite good.

392
00:18:14,110 --> 00:18:14,830
I like them.

393
00:18:21,310 --> 00:18:22,630
I mean

394
00:18:23,110 --> 00:18:23,990
I

395
00:18:24,670 --> 00:18:25,630
like you.

396
00:18:34,830 --> 00:18:36,190
What are you doing?

397
00:18:36,190 --> 00:18:39,830
I didn't say I'll move in.

398
00:18:40,990 --> 00:18:42,230
I didn't invite you.

399
00:18:43,230 --> 00:18:44,350
This is the spare key.

400
00:18:45,630 --> 00:18:46,550
Keep it for me.

401
00:18:47,950 --> 00:18:48,750
OK.

402
00:18:48,950 --> 00:18:51,470
I'll keep it for you reluctantly.

403
00:19:06,830 --> 00:19:07,870
What did you eat?

404
00:19:08,110 --> 00:19:09,390
Why are you so tall?

405
00:19:09,750 --> 00:19:10,710
What did you eat?

406
00:19:11,510 --> 00:19:12,670
Why haven't you grown taller?

407
00:20:06,830 --> 00:20:07,550
Xiao Tu.

408
00:20:08,870 --> 00:20:09,830
Wish you happy.

409
00:20:24,110 --> 00:20:24,790
Rabbit.

410
00:20:25,350 --> 00:20:26,110
Come here.

411
00:20:26,110 --> 00:20:28,190
What do you think of this company?

412
00:20:28,190 --> 00:20:29,870
They are recruiting interns.

413
00:20:30,870 --> 00:20:32,030
Is it too early

414
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:32,950
to focus on internship recruitment?

415
00:20:33,470 --> 00:20:35,590
I don't have many classes in the third academic year.

416
00:20:35,590 --> 00:20:37,430
So I want to work as an intern while studying.

417
00:20:41,870 --> 00:20:43,950
This company is in Beijing.

418
00:20:44,590 --> 00:20:47,230
Then I can get closer to Jia Siwen.

419
00:20:48,150 --> 00:20:49,710
So you don't want me anymore?

420
00:20:50,230 --> 00:20:52,870
That's not what I meant.

421
00:20:53,230 --> 00:20:55,070
You two have a tacit understanding.

422
00:20:58,150 --> 00:20:59,310
Hi, Jia Siwen.

423
00:20:59,670 --> 00:21:01,230
Look what we are doing.

424
00:21:01,430 --> 00:21:03,510
Xiao Tu and I are hanging out our quilts.

425
00:21:03,510 --> 00:21:06,230
