426
00:21:07,230 --> 00:21:08,550
Thank you.

427
00:21:08,710 --> 00:21:11,790
I feel like I'm dating my brother.

428
00:21:11,790 --> 00:21:12,990
Is it because I'm wearing the contact lens

429
00:21:12,990 --> 00:21:15,350
endorsed by your brother?

430
00:21:16,150 --> 00:21:16,830
What?

431
00:21:17,030 --> 00:21:20,030
I mean you are busier than my brother.

432
00:21:21,430 --> 00:21:22,470
I'm sorry.

433
00:21:24,030 --> 00:21:25,270
I miss you so much.

434
00:21:27,630 --> 00:21:29,270
Don't throw up on the quilt.

435
00:21:29,270 --> 00:21:30,470
You two continue.

436
00:21:31,070 --> 00:21:31,710
Juanjuan.

437
00:21:32,030 --> 00:21:33,750
The weather forecast says it will rain in Yunhai.

438
00:21:33,750 --> 00:21:35,870
Remember to bring your coat and an umbrella when you go out.

439
00:21:35,870 --> 00:21:36,710
Don't catch a cold.

440
00:21:37,350 --> 00:21:38,190
You too.

441
00:21:39,470 --> 00:21:40,710
I just saw the recruitment information of an entertainment company

442
00:21:40,710 --> 00:21:42,550
in Beijing.

443
00:21:42,630 --> 00:21:44,190
I want to give it a try.

444
00:21:44,350 --> 00:21:46,110
If I pass the interview,

445
00:21:46,110 --> 00:21:48,470
I can go to see you.

446
00:21:48,950 --> 00:21:50,310
It's too hard.

447
00:21:50,790 --> 00:21:52,470
I should go to Yunhai to see you more.

448
00:21:52,870 --> 00:21:54,910
It's okay. As long as we can meet,

449
00:21:55,070 --> 00:21:56,630
it's worth it no matter how hard it is.

450
00:21:57,390 --> 00:21:58,950
I'm going to buy two sets of clothes for the interview

451
00:21:58,950 --> 00:22:00,270
in the mall later.

452
00:22:00,270 --> 00:22:01,030
I'll send photos to you.

453
00:22:01,030 --> 00:22:01,990
Help me choose.

454
00:22:02,310 --> 00:22:02,950
Okay.

455
00:22:04,310 --> 00:22:04,910
Right.

456
00:22:05,310 --> 00:22:07,470
You still remember

457
00:22:07,470 --> 00:22:08,590
what day it is in several days, right?

458
00:22:09,870 --> 00:22:10,830
Your birthday.

459
00:22:10,990 --> 00:22:11,750
I won't forget.

460
00:22:11,990 --> 00:22:12,670
Jia Siwen.

461
00:22:12,950 --> 00:22:13,590
Get in.

462
00:22:14,070 --> 00:22:14,710
Coming.

463
00:22:15,390 --> 00:22:16,350
I have to go.

464
00:22:16,670 --> 00:22:17,270
Okay.

465
00:22:17,310 --> 00:22:18,510
Be careful.

466
00:22:35,430 --> 00:22:36,470
From this perspective, don't you think

467
00:22:36,470 --> 00:22:38,230
my legs won't look long enough in the photo?

468
00:22:38,230 --> 00:22:39,870
Your legs are long enough.

469
00:22:39,870 --> 00:22:41,350
I'm almost on the ground.

470
00:22:41,990 --> 00:22:42,950
Did you activate the beauty mode?

471
00:22:43,110 --> 00:22:43,830
Yes.

472
00:22:44,270 --> 00:22:44,870
Okay.

473
00:22:45,150 --> 00:22:45,870
Take a look.

474
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:49,470
OK.

475
00:22:49,470 --> 00:22:50,470
I'm sending it to Jia Siwen.

476
00:22:51,630 --> 00:22:53,630
I think the first one looks better.

477
00:22:53,870 --> 00:22:55,190
It doesn't matter what you think.

478
00:22:55,190 --> 00:22:57,830
What Jia Siwen thinks matters.

479
00:22:59,070 --> 00:22:59,830
Miss.

480
00:22:59,830 --> 00:23:01,230
Are you satisfied with any of the 28 suits

481
00:23:01,230 --> 00:23:02,550
you just tried on?

482
00:23:02,670 --> 00:23:04,430
In a minute. We are thinking about it.

483
00:23:12,870 --> 00:23:14,590
Is Jia Siwen busy?

484
00:23:15,110 --> 00:23:16,830
Why don't we take a look at something else first?

485
00:23:16,990 --> 00:23:18,830
I want to visit the home furniture store.

486
00:23:19,310 --> 00:23:20,150
Home furniture?

487
00:23:20,870 --> 00:23:22,350
You denied you are married

488
00:23:22,350 --> 00:23:23,870
and you said you wouldn't live together, right?

489
00:23:24,110 --> 00:23:24,830
What?

490
00:23:24,990 --> 00:23:27,110
Now you are acting like you are his wife.

491
00:23:28,110 --> 00:23:29,310
Go get changed.

492
00:23:29,310 --> 00:23:30,990
Go get changed.

493
00:23:31,310 --> 00:23:32,230
Everyone.

494
00:23:32,510 --> 00:23:33,750
After we go into the mountain,

495
00:23:33,750 --> 00:23:34,790
there might be no signal.

496
00:23:34,790 --> 00:23:36,230
You must hold the walkie-talkie.

497
00:23:36,230 --> 00:23:37,350
Follow the team closely.

498
00:23:37,390 --> 00:23:38,430
Don't act alone.

499
00:23:38,430 --> 00:23:39,230
Got it?

500
00:23:39,750 --> 00:23:40,470
Yes.

501
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:44,710
We're going to stay in the mountain for two days.

502
00:23:44,870 --> 00:23:46,110
There might be no signal.

503
00:23:46,190 --> 00:23:46,990
Don't worry.

504
00:23:55,590 --> 00:23:56,630
Okay. Everyone.

505
00:23:56,870 --> 00:23:57,790
It will be mountain roads ahead.

506
00:23:57,790 --> 00:23:58,990
We can't drive in.

507
00:23:59,070 --> 00:24:00,470
Pack your things

508
00:24:00,470 --> 00:24:02,470
and get off with me in an orderly manner.

509
00:24:10,270 --> 00:24:12,150
Come and get your stuff.

510
00:24:19,630 --> 00:24:20,670
So cute.

511
00:24:20,670 --> 00:24:21,590
Look at that bear.

512
00:24:22,510 --> 00:24:24,350
What do you want for your birthday?

513
00:24:24,950 --> 00:24:26,350
It shouldn't cost more than ten yuan.

514
00:24:27,630 --> 00:24:28,550
Don't worry.

515
00:24:28,550 --> 00:24:30,230
I don't expect much from you.

516
00:24:30,350 --> 00:24:32,790
I'm looking forward to Jia Siwen's gift.

517
00:24:32,830 --> 00:24:34,350
After all, this will be the first birthday

518
00:24:34,350 --> 00:24:35,470
after we were together.

519
00:24:36,230 --> 00:24:36,950
Fine.

520
00:24:57,630 --> 00:24:59,350
Has your virtual boyfriend replied to your message?

521
00:25:01,350 --> 00:25:02,150
No.

522
00:25:03,470 --> 00:25:04,710
It's okay. Let's go.

523
00:25:09,950 --> 00:25:10,630
Shuang.

524
00:25:10,710 --> 00:25:11,590
Check it first.

525
00:25:15,790 --> 00:25:16,550
Sir.

526
00:25:16,830 --> 00:25:18,870
Can I apply for a leave for an hour?

527
00:25:19,110 --> 00:25:20,590
I came in a hurry.

528
00:25:20,590 --> 00:25:22,230
I didn't have the time to tell my family.

529
00:25:22,350 --> 00:25:24,630
So I want to go up the mountain to look for the signal

530
00:25:24,630 --> 00:25:26,070
to see if I can send a message.

531
00:25:26,150 --> 00:25:28,230
But you can't go out now.

532
00:25:28,390 --> 00:25:30,350
They'll pick us up tomorrow morning.

533
00:25:33,910 --> 00:25:35,590
Okay, thank you.

534
00:25:41,230 --> 00:25:42,630
Do you remember that chemistry teacher?

535
00:25:42,630 --> 00:25:43,350
In junior high school.

536
00:25:45,590 --> 00:25:46,630
Siwen, where are you going?

537
00:25:48,430 --> 00:25:50,110
I'm going up the mountain to look for the signal.

538
00:25:50,110 --> 00:25:51,150
Don't go.

539
00:25:51,150 --> 00:25:52,670
The weather forecast says there will be showers tonight.

540
00:25:52,670 --> 00:25:53,350
