541
00:25:53,870 --> 00:25:54,710
It's okay.

542
00:25:55,350 --> 00:25:56,590
I'll be back soon.

543
00:25:56,590 --> 00:25:57,630
Rest early.

544
00:25:57,950 --> 00:25:58,950
Be careful.

545
00:26:16,950 --> 00:26:17,950
Master.

546
00:26:19,070 --> 00:26:19,950
Look.

547
00:26:20,510 --> 00:26:23,470
We're going to Shile for internship soon.

548
00:26:23,710 --> 00:26:25,750
Shouldn't we show

549
00:26:26,110 --> 00:26:27,910
team spirit?

550
00:26:32,190 --> 00:26:32,870
Zhu.

551
00:26:33,670 --> 00:26:34,710
Help me remember.

552
00:26:34,710 --> 00:26:36,670
Are the master and his three disciples in Journey to the West

553
00:26:36,670 --> 00:26:38,870
always together

554
00:26:38,870 --> 00:26:39,830
when they eat, sleep, drink, and walk?

555
00:26:40,110 --> 00:26:40,710
Yes.

556
00:26:42,590 --> 00:26:44,230
Monsters come to capture me frequently.

557
00:26:44,470 --> 00:26:46,110
It's normal that I don't live with you.

558
00:26:46,190 --> 00:26:47,950
That's not true, Master.

559
00:26:49,030 --> 00:26:52,190
If you can share your room with me in your apartment,

560
00:26:52,470 --> 00:26:54,470
