561
00:26:56,830 --> 00:26:57,870
Me too.

562
00:27:00,030 --> 00:27:00,670
OK.

563
00:27:01,990 --> 00:27:02,830
I'll find you

564
00:27:02,830 --> 00:27:04,270
a realtor in a few days.

565
00:27:04,630 --> 00:27:05,750
You can rent a house too.

566
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:08,830
Master.

567
00:27:09,190 --> 00:27:10,430
No need to bother with it.

568
00:27:10,870 --> 00:27:11,590
Think about it.

569
00:27:11,830 --> 00:27:13,630
Madam is busy with her studies.

570
00:27:13,630 --> 00:27:15,870
